NOTICE OF CLAIM OF LIEN FOR DELINQUENT ASSESSMENTS
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN: Red Rock Financial Services, has been assigned as agent by the Cottage
Grove Estates Homeowners Association, Inc (the "Association"), in accordance with Nevada Revised Statues
Chapter 116 and the Association's Covenants, Conditions, and Restrictions, as amended and/or annexed (the
"CC&Rs"), recorded on 07/18/2006, in Book Number , as Instrument Number 663149, of the Official Records
of Nye County, Nevada, which CC&Rs have been supplied to and agreed upon by said owner.
The Association imposes a Lien for Delinquent Assessments on the following property:
11 S Spruce Ln Pahrump NV 89048
COTTAGE GROVE ESTATES LOT 54 BLOCK 1 in the County of Nye
Current Owner(s) of Record for the property:
ANTAWN L. MCDONALD AND MARTHA LEĘ MCDONALD
The amount owing as of the date of preparation of this lien is ** $1,233.12.
This amount may include assessments, late fees, interest, fines/violations, including fine(s) for violation(s) of
the governing documents that pose an imminent threat of causing a substantial adverse effect on the health,
safety or welfare of the owners of 11 S Spruce Ln or the Association's residents, and collection fees and costs.
** The amount owing may increase or decrease as assessments, late fees, interest, fines/violations, collection fees,
costs or partial payments are applied to the account.
Dated: May 20, 2022 .-
Prepared By Olivia Kellogg as agent of Red Rock Financial Services on behalf of Cottage Grove Estates Homeowners
Association, Inc
STATE OF NEVADA
COUNTY OF CLARK
On May 20, 2022, before me, personally appeared Olivia Kellogg, personally known to me (or proved to me
on the basis of satisfactory evidence) to be the person whose name is subscribed to the within instrument and
acknowledged to me that they executed the same in their authorized capacity, and that by their signature on the
instrument the person, or the entity upon behalf of which the person acted, executed the instrument.
WITNESS my hand and official seal.
When Recorded Mail To: Red Rock Financial Services
770 E. Warm Springs Road Suite 320
Las Vegas, Nevada 89119
702-932-6887
Julia Thompson
Notary Public - State of Nevada
Appt. No. 08-7932-1
My Appt. Expires Sept. 04, 2024
